<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sign-n">sign <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /saɪn/    美 /saɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 符号：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a plus sign
加号</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 指示牌；标记：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>road</strong> / <strong>traffic sign</strong>
道路/交通标识</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sign says “No smoking”.
告示牌上写着“禁止吸烟”。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 手势；(头、手、眼等的) 示意动作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>sign language</strong>
手势语</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>made a sign</strong> to me to leave the room.
他打手势示意我离开房间。</p></div>

<h4 id="4-c-u">4.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 迹象；征兆：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The rainy weather <strong>showed no sign of</strong> improving.
雨还在下，没有转晴的迹象。</p></div></div>